Hydroxymethylglutaryl-CoA synthase, mitochondrial precursor
(EC 2.3.3.10) (HMG-CoA synthase) (3-hydroxy-3-methylglutaryl coenzyme
A synthase).
"The transcriptional landscape of the mammalian genome.";
"The status, quality, and expansion of the NIH full-length cDNA
project: the Mammalian Gene Collection (MGC).";
"Human mitochondrial HMG CoA synthase: liver cDNA and partial genomic
cloning, chromosome mapping to 1p12-p13, and possible role in
